---
layout: default
meta_description:
body_class: home
---

<section class="py-16 border-b border-grey-800">
  <div class="mx-auto px-8 max-w-6xl">

    <h1 class="mb-6 md:mb-10">{{ site.name }}</h1>
    <p class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-grey-600 font-800 leading-tight">Woont in Leeuwarden. Trotse â€˜heitâ€™ van Elin en Fedde. Vriend van Lotte. Hobbyâ€™s: wielrennen, muziek en koken. Werkt bij <a href="https://tres.nl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link text-yellow-800 hover:text-white">TRES</a>. Interesses: UX en Design Systems. 10+ jaar ervaring.</p>

    <img src="/images/home/tres.jpg" alt="" class="pt-6 sm:pt-12 mb-6">

  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 bg-black border-b border-grey-800">
  <div class="mx-auto px-8 max-w-6xl pb-4">

    <h2 class="mb-6">Blog</h2>
    {% for post in collections.blog %}

      {% set year = post.date | yearDisplay %}
      {% if year != prev_year %}
        <h4 class="text-grey-600 mb-2 mt-4 md:mt-6 font-900">{{year}}</h4>
      {% endif %}

      <h4 class="mb-2">
        <a class="pr-4 text-yellow-800 hover:text-white" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        <span class="block md:inline text-base md:text-xl whitespace-no-wrap">{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</span>
      </h4>

      {% set prev_year = post.date | yearDisplay %}
    {% endfor %}

  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 border-b border-grey-800">
  <div class="mx-auto pl-8 pr-4 max-w-6xl">

    <div class="flex flex-no-wrap justify-between items-end mb-6 md:mb-10 mr-4">
      <h2 class="flex-auto leading-none mb-0">Twitter</h2>
      <a href="https://twitter.com/dydric" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex-initial link bg-blue-800 hover:bg-white text-white hover:text-blue-800 font-800 rounded-full py-1 px-3 m-auto ml-6 text-sm sm:text-base">Follow me</a>
    </div>

    <h4 class="text-grey-600 mb-4 md:mb-6 mt-4 font-900">Recent:</h4>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap">
    {%- for i in range(0, 4) -%}
      {% set item = import.tweets[i] %}
      {% include "components/tweet.njk" %}
    {%- endfor -%}

    <h4 class="text-grey-600 mb-4 md:mb-6 mt-4 font-900">Likes:</h4>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap">
    {%- for i in range(0, 4) -%}
      {% set item = import.likes[i] %}
      {% include "components/likes.njk" %}
    {%- endfor -%}

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 bg-black border-b border-grey-800">
  <div class="mx-auto pl-8 max-w-6xl">

    <h2 class="mb-6 md:mb-10">Activiteiten</h2>

    <h4 class="text-grey-600 mb-4 md:mb-6 mt-4 font-900">Stappen:</h4>

    <div class="flex flex-no-wrap items-end mr-2 md:mr-0 mb-12 md:mb-16">
    {%- for i in range(0, 30) -%}
      {% set item = import.health[i] %}

      {%- set stepsclass = "bg-yellow-800" -%}
      {%- if item.steps >= 10000 -%}
        {%- set stepsclass = "bg-green-500" -%}
      {%- elif item.steps <= 5000 -%}
        {%- set stepsclass = "bg-red-500" -%}
      {%- endif -%}

      <div class="w1 flex-auto box mr-2 rounded-lg {{ stepsclass }}"
          style="height:{{ (item.steps / 100) | round }}px">
      </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
    </div>

    <h4 class="text-grey-600 mb-6 md:mb-8 mt-4 font-900">Workouts:</h4>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap">
      {%- for i in range(0, 8) -%}
        {% set item = import.workouts[i] %}

        <div class="w-1/2 md:w-1/4 pr-4 mb-6 font-800">
          <span class="block text-grey-600 text-sm md:text-base font-500 mb2">{{ item.type }}</span>
          <span class="block text-lg md:text-xl">{{ item.movingtime }}</span>
          {% if item.distance %}
            {%- set workoutkm = item.distance | int -%}
            <span class="block text-lg md:text-xl">{{ (workoutkm / 1000) | round(2) }}km</span>
          {% endif %}
          {% if item.heartrate %}
            <span class="inline-block text-base font-600 my-2 mr-2">â™¥ {{ item.heartrate }}</span>
          {% endif %}
          {% if item.activecalories %}
            <span class="inline-block text-base font-600 my-2">ðŸ’ª {{ item.activecalories }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
